%% B.A.D.D.I.E. — Voice Interaction Pipeline
%% End-to-end voice processing flow

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant VAD as Silero VAD
    participant STT as Whisper STT
    participant LLM as Gemini 3.1
    participant RAG as Memory (RAG)
    participant TTS as Piper/Kokoro
    participant A as 🎭 Avatar

    U->>VAD: Voice Audio Stream
    VAD->>STT: Speech Segment (endpoint detected)
    STT->>LLM: Transcribed Text
    RAG->>LLM: Retrieved Memories (context)
    LLM->>LLM: Generate Response (streaming)
    LLM-->>TTS: Sentence Buffer (first complete sentence)
    LLM-->>A: Emotional Tone + Phonemes
    TTS->>U: Audio Output (overlapped with generation)
    A->>U: Lip-sync + Expression Animation
